      "description": "Clean, good-condition vehicle that runs and drives well and should make a solid daily driver or weekend cruiser. It presents nicely overall, with a well-kept appearance, but it\u2019s not flawless\u2014expect some normal light cosmetic wear, small paint or body imperfections, and an interior that shows moderate age-appropriate use. Overall, this is an honest, well-sorted car that feels a step above a basic driver and should appeal to someone looking for a dependable, good-looking example without paying top-dollar showroom pricing.",
