      "description": "A practical, budget-friendly vehicle that offers straightforward transportation at an accessible price point. This car shows its age and is best suited for a value-focused buyer seeking dependable basic use, a backup vehicle, or a project opportunity. Priced to reflect condition while still delivering real-world usefulness, it represents an honest chance to get on the road without overspending.",
