      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car is being sold in poor condition, so I want to be upfront about it\u2014but for the right buyer, it could make a great project, parts car, or cheap runaround. It\u2019s a straightforward opportunity to pick up a vehicle without spending a fortune. If you\u2019re handy, practical, or just need something budget-friendly to work with, this could be a solid fit. Priced to sell and ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 3900.0,
