      "description": "Built for someone who appreciates honest, old-school mechanical feel, this car starts, runs, and offers a solid foundation for a budget commuter, shop truck, or weekend project. It shows its age cosmetically and will want attention in a few areas, but the drivetrain still delivers dependable operation and the chassis has the kind of straightforward serviceability enthusiasts look for. If you want an affordable vehicle with usable bones, strong parts availability, and plenty of upside for the next owner, this one is worth a look.",
